-   **Student Authentication**: Secure login using Roll Number and Password (validated against `students.csv`).
-   **Photo Processing**: Built-in image cropper to ensure perfect passport-size photos for the ID card.
-   **High-Resolution Output**: Generates **A4 Landscape (3508 x 2480 px @ 300 DPI)** certificates suitable for high-quality printing.
-   **Dynamic ID Card**: Automatically generates a student ID card on the certificate with:
    -   Student Photo
    -   QR Code (links to a digital verification URL)
    -   **Smart Text Fitting**: Automatically adjusts font size and wraps text for long names to fit perfectly.
